(16, 1, '2024-03-05 13:19:45', '2024-03-05 13:19:45', '[page_header align=\"center\" title_size=\"xlarge\" title_case=\"uppercase\" bg_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)\" class=\"page-single\"]\n\n[row style=\"small\"]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>TOGO is a more than 15+ years old leading manufacturing and engineering company of China providing integrated design, supply, installation, and project management services for organic waste management.</p>\n<p>The expanding list of satisfied clients reflects our ability to execute challenging projects. Difficult weather or terrain has been no deterrent to our team which has delivered consistently and brought accolades to the company. The high percentage of repeat orders stand testimony to this. As a reflection of our international quality standards, manufacturing, and project management techniques, TOGO holds CE, ISO9001, ISO45001, and ISO14001 certification. Thousands of our satisfied clientele of renowned Industrial Organisations in the Private as well as Government sector are spread over to the entire section of China and abroad.</p>\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"192\" image_size=\"original\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<p>TOGO work with some of the world’s leading brands to implement a zero-waste solution in their operations. Our clients are able to minimize their waste to landfills, reduce their greenhouse gas emissions and thus reduce their overall environmental footprint.</p>\n<p><strong>Vision &amp; Mission</strong></p>\n<p>TOGO’s vision is to become a reputable company to consistently deliver beyond the expected quality by its customers while earning competitive returns. TOGO always aims at providing appropriate solutions in the organic waste management segment. In meeting our customer’s needs everything we do is of high quality in pursuit of a continuous improvement process. We consistently strive to deliver high-quality and latest technology products and services.</p>\n<p>Our multi-skilled and highly adaptable workforce is capable of handling multiple complex projects across the world. We believe in making available innovative and cost-effective engineering solutions for our customers.</p>\n<h5><strong>Countries of Export</strong></h5>\n<p>TOGO has exported our products and equipment to hundreds of countries and regions, including Portugal, Spain, France, Italy, Poland, Germany, United Kingdom, Russia, Canada, United States, Thailand, Malaysia, Singapore, Philippines, India, Maldives, Sri Lanka, Turkey, United Arab Emirates, Saudi Arabia, Oman, South Africa, Chile, Brazil, Peru, Argentina, Australia, and a few more.</p>\n<h5><strong>INFRASTRUCTURE</strong></h5>\n<p>Our manufacturing unit is spread over 10,000 sq. feet and is capable of manufacturing equipment in compliance with the most stringent requirements of various countries. The plant is well equipped with the latest machinery for material handling and top-quality fabrication. We have earned a good name by manufacturing international quality equipment and maintaining the highest levels of quality is our ultimate aim.</p>\n<p>TOGO has enhanced its manufacturing capacity by adding Laser cutting machines, Plasma cutting, Vertical Machining Centers, and all other machines for bending, rolling, cutting, and machines that are CNC with the latest welding and finishing equipment. An advanced in-house tool room helps meet the high-quality norms of our rapidly growing customer base. We also have the latest CAD center for designing.</p>\n<p>TOGO focuses on developing cost-effective and reliable solutions for its customers and new product development is a continuous ongoing process with the strong R&amp;D Division. TOGO will give your business a boost into the circular economy, where both the planet and your profit margin can benefit from the application of innovative environmental technology.</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[section]\n\n[row style=\"small\" h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"CERTIFICATIONS\" tag_name=\"h2\" color=\"rgb(80, 158, 47)\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n[ux_gallery ids=\"129,127,125,123,121,120\" style=\"none\" lightbox=\"false\" type=\"slider\" columns=\"5\" slider_nav_style=\"circle\" slider_bullets=\"true\"]\n\n\n[/section]\n[section]\n\n[row style=\"small\" h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"FACTORY DISPLAY\" tag_name=\"h2\" color=\"rgb(80, 158, 47)\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[ux_video]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'Về chúng tôi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 've-chung-toi', '', '', '2024-03-07 09:29:24', '2024-03-07 09:29:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/togo/?page_id=16', 0, 'page', '', 0),
