(18, 1, '2024-03-05 13:20:12', '2024-03-05 13:20:12', '[page_header align=\"center\" title_size=\"xlarge\" title_case=\"uppercase\" bg_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)\" class=\"page-single\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[contact-form-7 id=\"243\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<h5>CONTACT TOGO</h5>\n<p>Our passionate team is here to help you with all your composting needs, and ensure you order the right solution, for the best price.</p>\n<p>If you would like to find out more about Composters or place an order for your business, please contact us today:</p>\n<h5>Contact Details</h5>\n<p>Email: info@togocomposter.com<br />Mobile/WhatsApp: +86 139 0615 3006</p>\n<p><strong>Opening Hours</strong><br />Monday to Friday 9 am to 6 pm</p>\n<p><strong>Address</strong><br />Head Office: 86-4-704, DiCui Road, Wuxi, Jiangsu, China<br />Factory: Southern District of Wanshi Industrial Park, Yixing, China</p>\n<p><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></p>\n<p>Hello, welcome to our website! We value your privacy very much and promise to protect your personal information when using our website. We will take all necessary measures to protect your personal information and will not disclose it to third parties unless required by law or with your explicit consent. Our privacy policy explains how we collect, use, process, store, and protect personal information. If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please feel free to contact us.</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]', 'Liên hệ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lien-he', '', '', '2024-03-07 09:33:28', '2024-03-07 09:33:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/togo/?page_id=18', 0, 'page', '', 0),
