(126, 1, '2024-03-06 09:48:53', '2024-03-06 09:48:53', 'TOGO premier food waste recycling machine helps your organization manage your food waste with ease. Our vision is to offer a machine that is easy, durable, strong, hygienic, with elegant design, and helps reclaim profits. Specifically designed for large buildings with limited space such as hotels, hospitals, schools, or universities and for residential perimeters such as condominiums, townhomes, municipalities, or villages, our machine simply converts your food waste to valuable materials within 24 hours automatically. It can be further configured to suit any layout of your building and your desired end-products.\r\n\r\n<strong>Response to Circular Economy</strong>\r\n\r\nTOGO food waste composters operate by automatic function with safety system, low maintenance cost. It turns organic waste into valuable materials that respond to “Circular economy, helps reduced waste-to-landfill and to let your organization achieve the zero-waste goal as well as in line with Sustainable Development Goals: SDGs from UN.\r\n\r\nOur machine saves your energy cost and space for air-conditioned storage as well as disposal cost if any. The materials after being processed can be sold or pelletized before sold, as animal feedstocks, organic fertilizers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Waste Recycling Machine Features:</strong>\r\n\r\n– Convert Food and Garden Waste to Fertilizer in 24 hours\r\n– No full-time manpower is required\r\n– PLC based Touch screen interface\r\n– Compact design with Wheels for mobility\r\n– Feed &amp; Forget system\r\n– Compact and Mobile\r\n\r\n<strong>Key Technology of TOGO Composters:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>STERILIZING system: “Patents” all pathogens, germs, bacteria, viruses are going to be killed during the drying process with high temperature.</li>\r\n 	<li>MORE THAN 10% REDUCE ORGANIC WASTE TO VALUE MATERIAL.</li>\r\n 	<li>DE-ODORIZING: Patents that are implemented for the products so the odor is completely blocked and there is no odor around the types of machinery.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Waste can be put in:</strong> Vegetable Leaves, Leftovers, Vegetable Peel, Fish, Meat, Shrimp Shell, Crab Shell, Egg Shell, Small Bones, Bread, Coffee Grounds, etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Prohibited:</strong> Plastic Products, Metals, Ceramics, Fuel Oil, Solvents, Large Wood, Large Animal Bones, Cloth and other domestic waste and hazardous waste.', 'TG-CC-200 Waste Recycling Machine', '<strong>Waste Recycling Machine</strong> can divert organic waste from landfills and produce fertilizer for landscaping, gardening, or farming.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tg-cc-200-waste-recycling-machine', '', '', '2024-03-07 07:35:39', '2024-03-07 07:35:39', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/togo/?post_type=product&#038;p=126', 0, 'product', '', 0),
