(128, 1, '2024-03-06 09:49:35', '2024-03-06 09:49:35', 'TOGO organic waste converter is an automatic composting system. Our patented system rapidly processes organic waste into rich compost. The system is easy to install and requires minimal training for operation. Just fill it, shut it, forget it and in just 24 hours, TOGO treats your organic waste. TOGO is a completely stand-alone unit, designed for easy input and output. It is completely automated and requires minimal intervention and training to operate.\r\n\r\nWith the boom in population, every day we generate lakhs of metric tons of garbage in the world. Waste management is one of the rising concerns of the world today, for saving its environment. We can very easily transform the organic food wastes into fertilizers and mineral-rich soil with the help of Bio-Degradable organic food waste electric converter machines.\r\n\r\nTOGO has come up, with its sturdy and well-organized organic waste composting machine that is meant for commercial purposes. Fully automatic, neat, and compact. They are one-site portable machines and are also equipped with cut-edge PLC technology. All the TOGO’s composter machines can compost any type of raw organic waste, and turn it into fertilizer reducing 90% of volume, using minimal energy. The whole composting process is odor-free and these machines can be installed at restaurants, apartments, hostels, malls, airports, canteens, and by catering agencies.\r\n\r\n<strong>Unique Features:</strong>\r\n– Our Waste composting organic machines are compact, space-saving, energy-saving and need little to no amount manual labor.\r\n– It can be installed easily, and the maintenance of the machine is also hassle-free.\r\n– The Electric compositing machines are based on PLC technologies and are fully automatic.\r\n– It has one-touch features in it.\r\n– It processes organic food wastes in less than a day’s time.\r\n– No emission will spill from it; neither smoke nor odour.\r\n– The Electric food waste converter is highly hygienic. It checks the breeding of bacteria, additives, or water requirements.\r\n\r\n<strong>Waste can be put in:</strong> Vegetable Leaves, Leftovers, Vegetable Peel, Fish, Meat, Shrimp Shell, Crab Shell, Egg Shell, Small Bones, Bread, Coffee Grounds, etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Prohibited:</strong> Plastic Products, Metals, Ceramics, Fuel Oil, Solvents, Large Wood, Large Animal Bones, Cloth and other domestic waste and hazardous waste.', 'TG-CC-300 Organic', '<strong>Organic Waste Converter</strong> is a pioneering machine that offers easy, fast, and efficient treatment to your segregated organic waste.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tg-cc-300-organic-waste-converter', '', '', '2024-03-07 07:35:33', '2024-03-07 07:35:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/togo/?post_type=product&#038;p=128', 0, 'product', '', 0),
