(191, 1, '2024-03-07 03:19:42', '2024-03-07 03:19:42', 'With the rapid development of the company and the continuous innovation and improvement of the equipment research and development capabilities, TOGO’s intelligent food waste and kitchen waste processing equipment has steadily developed in the domestic market while also expanding the international market, attracting a large number of foreign customers to visit and discuss cooperation.\r\n\r\nOn May 15, 2023, customers from Ireland visited Wuxi Tangu factory, foreign trade department, and overseas business department to inspect and negotiate. The general manager, deputy general manager, and overseas business department manager and staff of the company expressed a warm welcome to the international friends who came from afar and gave them a cordial reception.\r\n\r\nAccompanied by the relevant person in charge of Wuxi Tangu, Irish customers visited the factory, project site, overseas business department, and fully understood the company’s corporate culture, development history, and various models of equipment. Mechanical, electrical engineers, and overseas business department managers answered various questions raised by customers in detail. TOGO’s food waste and kitchen waste processing equipment’s production process, quality control, after-sales team all impressed the customers.\r\n\r\nAfter the visit, Irish customers had an in-depth discussion with our company on cooperation matters. They said that they were very happy to have the opportunity to visit TOGO factory and thanked our company for their warm and thoughtful reception. They also said that this visit was not only for negotiating cooperation matters, but also for understanding TOGO’s production scale, visiting the equipment operation site in person, and being impressed by our company’s good working environment and orderly work process, as well as the equipment’s operation effect. TOGO, as a preferred supplier, will give more cooperation and orders in the face of future markets.\r\n\r\nThe visit of Irish customers not only strengthened the communication between our company and international customers but also laid a solid foundation for our TOGO intelligent food waste and kitchen waste processing equipment to better explore the international market.\r\n\r\nIn the future, we will always adhere to integrity-based, quality-oriented principles, actively expand domestic and foreign market share, and continuously improve and develop.', '[Cross-border investigation and cooperation] Warmly welcome Irish customers to visit and discuss cooperation!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cross-border-investigation-and-cooperation-warmly-welcome-irish-customers-to-visit-and-discuss-cooperation', '', '', '2024-03-07 03:19:42', '2024-03-07 03:19:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/togo/?p=191', 0, 'post', '', 0),
